  "texts": [
    "They together bypass the pretrained LLMs' safeguard.",
    "To investigate how each objective helps, we have two ablations: ATLA without L s, which removes the I-awareness objective, and ATLA without L e, which replaces the weighted loss with mean loss.",
    "In Fig. 3, we show the learning efficiency of the adversarial suffixes on each pretrained LLM for every ablations.",
    "To achieve the maximum attack success rate, an ideal objective for adversarial suffix learning is to optimize the suffix X to encourage the probability of all possible affirmative formats.",
    "However, it is impractical due to the infinite property of the affirmative response set."
  ]
